<p>Seems to me you're missing some valuable conjectures.</p>
<p>Q: How did this older version foundation agent get info we don't have now?<br />
A: Easy. He is not one of ours. Multi world universes will include those that don't differ from ours. This agent is not from &quot;here&quot;.</p>
<p>Q: How does he know what's happened 300 years ago?<br />
